+## How to Test
+
+### Prerequisites
+
+1. **OpenSearch with Security Plugin**
+   - Must be running with passkey authentication enabled
+   - Backend APIs must be accessible at `/_plugins/_security/passkey/*`
+
+2. **HTTPS or Localhost**
+   - WebAuthn requires secure context (HTTPS or localhost)
+
+### Start Dashboards
+
+```bash
+cd dashboards-security
+yarn install
+yarn start
+```
+
+### Test Login Flow
+
+1. Navigate to login page
+2. Look for "Sign in with Passkey" button
+3. Click button
+4. Enter username
+5. Click "Continue"
+6. Use Touch ID/Face ID/Windows Hello or security key
+7. Should redirect to Dashboards home
+
+### Test Registration Flow
+
+1. Navigate to passkey management page
+2. Click "Register New Passkey"
+3. Enter friendly name (e.g., "My iPhone")
+4. Click "Register"
+5. Use Touch ID/Face ID/Windows Hello or security key
+6. Should see success toast and new passkey in list
+
+### Test Management Flow
+
+1. View list of registered passkeys
+2. Click delete icon on a passkey
+3. Confirm deletion
+4. Should see success toast and passkey removed from list
